# Prompt Engineering Rules

- System prompts live in `prompts/system/`; domain prompts in `prompts/<domain>/`.
- Use Jinja2 templates in `prompts/templates/` for variable substitution.
- Few-shot examples in `prompts/few_shots/` — versioned per agent.
- Never include PII or secrets in prompt templates.
- RAG context injected via `prompts/rag/` templates with citation placeholders.
- Keep prompts under 4000 tokens; summarize long context via `memory/summary_memory.py`.
